          "description": "The provider I saw, Amy, was very kind and thorough and made me feel confident in the treatment plan. The rest of the team was also very nice, efficient, and helpful. I had an issue accessing my labs after my visit and Shanae and Daniel helped me resolve it quickly. Overall the experience was better than a typical urgent care visit and I would return to this location now that I know they are so great here.",
