          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVkhEy_NHgaGSSeCeL-X6u7AawwArCHc3rFUQeZZL7zHyq9bZy3=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "The clinic is conveniently located, tastefully decorated and had amenities like tea for customers. It was possible to make an appointment online, which was easy to get. The team was professional and helpful and provided me with services other clicks would not. They really helped me out in an urgent situation.  I would absolutely recommend this clinic to friends",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21Kc016bDNXV3RoWm5rMmJrSm9ZMU5vVnpKWk5sRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x70a0591820f88fe6!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOmJsMzl3WWthZnk2bkJoY1NoVzJZNlE%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "2 months ago",
