        {
          "username": "Joe Citro",
          "rating": 4,
          "contributor_id": "101546501329330130904",
          "user_review_count": 9,
          "user_photo_count": 0,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWkIoJtN_MI5_veGHlMz13H_quW8yPeRTyiTwuX1ULfCJ7CCVs=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "As a walk in, the wait was reasonable. The gentleman at the front desk was kind personable, and did what he could to get me in soon. Kudos.\nThe only complaint is that the PA's examination results did not match the conclusion written in the report.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tVNExUZzBiREV5Tkd4WGRXdFRSbGxNVFZoSmNVRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x70a0591820f88fe6!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOkU4LTg0bDEyNGxXdWtTRllMTVhJcUE%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "a month ago",
          "date_iso8601": "2026-05-01T17:06:40+00:00"
        },
        {
          "username": "Elyse Grossman",
          "rating": 5,
          "contributor_id": "101475665047846098797",
          "user_review_count": 14,
          "user_photo_count": 3,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocICRDOGLrrfgY00eYC4mv_ld7c8J8gJudAX7r1XwO2AFFOO7g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "Probably one of the best instacare experiences I\u2019ve ever had. I made an appointment and they brought me right into a room, no wait. The medical assistant was incredibly kind and explained everything to me he even was very nice when I nearly vomited on him during a strep test. The PA was also super friendly and explained everything to me, and helped me understand what meditation i needed.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xsZlZFdFdWRGh4VWs5bloySXplRzVLTkZkTk0zYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x70a0591820f88fe6!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOllfVEtWVDhxUk9nZ2IzeG5KNFdNM3c%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "5 months ago",
          "date_iso8601": "2026-01-24T03:10:58+00:00"
        },
        {
          "username": "Jasmine Thorson",
          "rating": 1,
          "contributor_id": "101856350855963228864",
          "user_review_count": 13,
          "user_photo_count": 4,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVYcJfJMMrg0DmDgNN5Ti5eczcEfBjL_vkPrH5EXKdw7myk0gvoEQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "Absolute worst urgent care experience ever. I have a deep splinter I can\u2019t get out myself, after charging me $50 and making me wait an hour they took a couple little looks at it and said \u201cwe can\u2019t help you cuz we can\u2019t see it on the surface, you should go to a podiatrist\u201d what kind of provider can\u2019t dig out a sliver? What an absolute joke. DO NOT go here. So incredibly disappointed.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25BNGIxTlZVamhSUXpoeWIzcFRWVXBpU0hCU2VWRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x70a0591820f88fe6!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOnA4b1NVUjhRQzhyb3pTVUpiSHBSeVE%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "a month ago",
          "date_iso8601": "2026-05-02T15:03:47+00:00"
        },
        {
          "username": "H6USS",
          "rating": 5,
          "contributor_id": "113453312462949657301",
          "user_review_count": 4,
          "user_photo_count": 0,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIjrpvEVoddBj0u5o4Dl6yA-DMDgW0P7ukWtvLjzZbWEEX_7A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "Another excellent experience! The nicest and most helpful, caring PA and assistant and even the receptionist was great and helpful! The PA Amy was excellent! She was kind, caring and very thorough with the care plan and details! Would never go to any other urgent care. They take you on time and really listen to the problem and your concerns and provide excellent care without rushing you. Thank you to Northwell and this excellent team and facility!",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s1SU5WaFdUR05WYkdwbmRsVmFVM0pFYjBaSVUxRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x70a0591820f88fe6!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOk5INVhWTGNVbGpndlVaU3JEb0ZIU1E%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "Edited 6 months ago",
          "date_iso8601": "2025-12-25T02:55:10+00:00"
        },
        {
          "username": "Marisa Beckley",
          "rating": 5,
          "contributor_id": "117968801268493332995",
          "user_review_count": 14,
          "user_photo_count": 10,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVaMx3J3wEygPR66CrwwTV03F7QN67vgVfiWDTxWwg4X593r8Hm=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "Very positive experience. After signing up for a slot online, I came in, checked in quickly, and was seen after just a couple minutes in the waiting room. Team was thorough and the on-call who assessed my issue was thorough and accurate. I was referred to a specialist who confirmed the diagnosis that Amy had predicted. I would absolutely return here if the need ever arises and I\u2019m in the area. Thank you all!",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21Gd05GbGhUREZKVVZGSWFYYzJWRmxEYURsUkxXYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x70a0591820f88fe6!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOmFwNFlhTDFJUVFIaXc2VFlDaDlRLWc%7C%7C?hl=en",
